            <p>
                The EventBus is used as a publish/subscribe event mechanism that lets objects communicate with eachother in a loosely coupled way.<br/>
		It offers event subscription based on event name, event class or for specific topics. An interception mechanism is in place to block or alter incoming events.
            </p>
            
            <p>
            	The library is thoroughly tested and is being used in the
